E-10 PURCHASE PART SIZE IS NOT INPUT
E-11 NAME CODE THAT INPUT IS NOT REGISTERED IN PART NAME M/F
E-12 UPD INST- CAN NOT INPUT COPIED CUSTOMER EXCEPT ADDTION.
E-13 UPD INST- CAN NOT INPUT COPIED FACTORY EXCEPT ADDTION.
